<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_01f90564-2135-48ba-b46d-81ea83e9d64b" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><sptc>I4D9</sptc><title id="_fa4b1b23-28f7-4a30-be1d-dafdb31ad4e4">Emergency lighting requirements</title><subclause id="_b30a1677-e0a8-4343-9e15-f31a432418bb" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_82ed7f99-ea7c-455f-869d-9084ce8f6724">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>An emergency lighting system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2827_2.3.0.xml#_8d4e5213-2e19-4a0c-b55a-e8afe0bcfa17" id="_cb87840a-98ab-4530-b8f6-85dbe6006afe" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">E4D2</xref> must be installed in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_229ecc65-161b-4025-a57d-2192202c951a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref> except that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_859d68b8-182c-4b02-90e6-9264e4973b3e">emergency lighting is not required at ground floor level in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2468_0.7.0.xml#_77fc5383-ae28-4bfd-ad12-0d5735cf1366" id="_c4a75110-f6cd-497e-a155-e2cb0895a49a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">cell type silos</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2474_25.0.0.xml#_638ea3e1-f483-40cc-9e79-5291637c5f3e" id="_ce2fc261-5990-4062-806a-1219169cab23" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storage sheds</xref>; and</li><li id="_be78ca76-4ae8-4421-a87e-96dcf8989245">the spacing of emergency lights can be increased to twice the distance required for Class 7 building.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_c1c9526b-4bd0-462c-a75d-5d882772972c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2a22af70-1ec2-45e3-a172-0f02253bc89b">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>An emergency lighting system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2827_2.3.0.xml#_8d4e5213-2e19-4a0c-b55a-e8afe0bcfa17" id="_f0eb0cb7-5906-4854-8b7f-e606f1da208c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">E4D2</xref> must be installed in an underground passage in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_5dbc6851-aa92-4882-a101-5aefa41681c0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>.</p></subclause></clause>